data.description: Welcome to 251 Columbus in West Harrison! This two-unit property offers versatility in living arrangements and rental income. The home features newly renovated kitchens that offer modern amenities and appeal to potential buyers/renters. Oversized bedrooms provide comfortable sleeping spaces for occupants. Freshly renovated bathrooms offer modern and stylish fixtures and amenities.The hardwood floors throughout provide durability, aesthetics, and easy maintenance. Driveway space and a 2-car garage provide ample parking options as well. The white picket fence and eye-catching landscaping adds charm and curb appeal to the property. The abundance of natural light and sun room offer bright and comfortable living spaces. Close proximity to highways makes commuting convenient, and close proximity to shopping offers convenience and easy access to amenities.
